resourceInfo.abstract:
FY2016
Planning scenarios will allow the GBLCC to develop a scenario planning document to visualize multidimensional scenarios. By using a participatory modeling process, the scenarios produced are managementrelevant and will have buyin from all major stakeholders. This management tool is a critical component of successful scenario planning. Using this vendor will allow stakeholders to share scenarios and impact assessments using normal email and social media tools, and allow you to continuously track progress towards process benchmarks

citation.title: Flaxman 2016 - Using Alternative Futures Modeling to produce management-relevant scenarios in the Western Great Basin
